{"tid":2290861,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"浴袍照曝光！子瑜飯店「害羞到蓋被子」大轉型性感露小蠻腰","createTime":"2020-11-18T10:32:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T13:23:30.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"180a3d2febc094376b3139677c4bea16a38c08ab","tid":2290861,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T10:32:01.000Z","msg":"南韓人氣女團「TWICE」靠著亮眼的外型，與甜美的歌聲，從選秀節目出道後便爆紅，其中台灣成員子瑜更是時常成為粉絲討論的話題，在台灣人氣度超高，上個月發行第二張正規專輯《Eyes wide open》這次公開拍攝年曆花絮，周子瑜穿起方領低胸上衣，扣子下方還有兩片延長的透膚下擺，衣服隨風吹起意外露出小蠻腰！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/18/2888864-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F18%2F2888864-PH.jpg&h=9fbfd3a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲周子瑜拍年曆花絮。（圖／翻攝自Twice YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/18/2888865-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F18%2F2888865-PH.jpg&h=5e310c66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲周子瑜（右一）和成員們一起蓋棉被拍年曆。（圖／翻攝自Twice YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n這次TWICE的年曆拍攝場景分為室內和室外，周子瑜和隊長志效一起在飯店床上打鬧，蓋著被子遮住下半部臉，靈動大眼超級無辜又具有成熟魅力！室外拍攝更是一到遊艇上拍攝，以「白色」為穿搭的主軸，周子瑜以接近露肩的大寬領剪裁微露酥胸，一雙大長腿穿上牛仔褲，以攝影師的角度拍攝起來，看起來更顯修長！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/18/2888866-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F18%2F2888866-PH.jpg&h=c7d36a67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲周子瑜（右）與志效（左）大打枕頭戰。（圖／翻攝自Twice YouTube）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/18/2888863-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F18%2F2888863-PH.jpg&h=b684c625&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲周子瑜超低胸上衣拍攝年曆。（圖／翻攝自Twice YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n周子瑜更是這組年曆拍攝中唯一一位以褲裝造型亮相的成員，相比其他成員都是連身白色洋裝居多，周子瑜的短版上衣可以拉到肩膀下方，直接變成一字領，外加一截透膚下擺，隨風吹起，直接露出白皙腰間與肚臍，根本性感與可愛全都兼具！"},{"pid":"bc9a69db6983aabaaeb84d1df2b5037f34e78780","tid":2290861,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T10:32:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/18/2888868-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F18%2F2888868-PH.jpg&h=95a54161&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲周子瑜在遊艇上擺拍pose，畫面超級養眼。（圖／翻攝自Twice YouTube）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/18/2888870-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F18%2F2888870-PH.jpg&h=b4c3ec4b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da8ec9aaac4125a82e44d74553763fb0fbd38339","tid":2290861,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T10:32:55.000Z","msg":"我夜晚捐入定延張被<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bde2e65f62ada1ce23db2617b3c091d107290061","tid":2290861,"uid":368098,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T10:33:03.000Z","msg":"定延交比我吧 其他自便<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16e5d99c312ff7cfb6b9e4b6dd3d65130b2bd442","tid":2290861,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T10:34:15.000Z","msg":"我同腎一齊枕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a5dc89d8835ace62e827174affeb60e729d6956","tid":2290861,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bde2e65f62ada1ce23db2617b3c091d107290061","tid":2290861,"uid":368098,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T10:33:03.000Z","msg":"定延交比我吧 其他自便<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T10:34:44.000Z","msg":"好 我要彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf49a344869bc902f9d1885ab72a394434c2a827","tid":2290861,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16e5d99c312ff7cfb6b9e4b6dd3d65130b2bd442","tid":22908